Here is the correct patch:

```diff
--- a/ext/libxml/libxml.c
+++ b/ext/libxml/libxml.c
@@ -1309,8 +1309,15 @@ PHP_LIBXML_API void php_libxml_node_decrement_resource(php_libxml_node_object *object)
